{"type":"message","id":"e5d3f3ad","parentId":"17e8f249","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:45:20.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Tushare token 已配置，但用户说\"查看我的股票\"太模糊，需要先问清楚具体要查哪些股票。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，想查看您的自选股，还是大盘指数行情？请告诉我具体股票代码（如 600519.SH、000858.SZ），我可以帮您获取实时行情。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773035119637}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a0641d9","parentId":"e5d3f3ad","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:52:15.257Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55d24e2cf0b0b492380b2873a97\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 13:52 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55d24e2cf0b0b492380b2873a97]\nou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5: 查看我的股票"}],"timestamp":1773035535255}}
{"type":"message","id":"def1dd7d","parentId":"3a0641d9","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:52:19.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次请求查看股票，我需要先确认他的自选股列表。检查是否有存储的自选股配置文件或历史记忆信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，我先帮您获取 A 股大盘实时行情：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_14873c80676343c1b5bf8ee8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\npro = ts.pro_api(os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN'))\n\n# 获取大盘指数实时行情\ndf = pro.index_realtime(ts_code=['000001.SH', '399001.SZ', '000300.SH'], fields='ts_code,name,pre_close,close,change,pct_chg')\nprint(\"=== A 股大盘指数 ===\")\nfor idx, row in df.iterrows():\n    print(f\"{row['ts_code']} {row['name']}: {row['close']} ({row['change']:+.2f}, {row['pct_chg']:+.2f}%)\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773035535257}}
